What works?
-----------

- bugzilla login

- bugzilla info -p
- bugzilla info -c PRODUCT

- (Create a bug)                    bugzilla new -p "Merge Request" -v "N/A" -c "Pardus Kurumsal 2" -l "initial comment" -s "test bug"
- (Modify a bug and add a comment)  bugzilla modify -l "Comment added" 17241

What should be fixed?
---------------------

- bugzilla -v PRODUCT

- (Change resolution to ASSIGNED)   bugzilla modify -k "ASSIGNED" -l "Test ASSIGNED" 17241
- (Assign to X)                     bugzilla modify --assignee=scirit@pardus.org.tr -l "Assign to Semen Cirit" 17241
- (Add X to CC)                     bugzilla modify --cc=scirit@pardus.org.tr -l "Add Semen to CC list" 17241
- (Change to RESOLVED:WONTFIX)      bugzilla modify -k "RESOLVED" -s "WONTFIX" -l "WONTFIX test" 17241
